  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub. NEEDS A HERO IMAGE: a screenshot of the TUI / crackintro-aesthetic editor in action. Draft. -->\n<p class=\"\">A TUI (and cross-platform Tauri desktop app) tool for editing Subway Builder save files, supporting both JSON and <code class=\"md-inline-code\">.metro</code> binary formats with auto-backup. Lets you edit money, game time, train count, and ticket price through an interactive terminal interface with a crackintro aesthetic.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Metro Savefile Doctor — current game analysis\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/metro-savefile-doctor/ui-1.png\" alt=\"Metro Savefile Doctor — current game analysis\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/metro-savefile-doctor/ui-1.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/metro-savefile-doctor/ui-1.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/metro-savefile-doctor/ui-1.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/metro-savefile-doctor/ui-1.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Metro Savefile Doctor — current game analysis\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1400\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.89deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2000×1400\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Editing a save file&#x27;s stats\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/metro-savefile-doctor/ui-2.png\" alt=\"Editing a save file&#x27;s stats\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w